snippet: Zach Randolph had 25 points and 13 rebounds, and the Memphis Grizzlies overcame a 21-point deficit in the second half to defeat the Boston Celtics 101-98 on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: Zach Randolph had 25 points and 13 rebounds, and the Memphis Grizzlies overcame a 21-point deficit in the second half to defeat the Boston Celtics 101-98 on Sunday.

headline.main: Randolph Leads Grizzlies to 101-98 Win Over Celtics
headline.print_headline: Randolph Leads Grizzlies to 101-98 Win Over Celtics
